            "title": "Old Testament Reading",
            "api_nlt_to_ref": "Deuteronomy.4:1-49",
            "value": "%3Cdiv%20class%3D%22%20NLT%20NLT%20BibleText%20section%22%3E%3Csection%3E%3Ch2%20class%3D%22bk_ch_vs_header%22%3EDeuteronomy%204%3A1-49%2C%20NLT%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22deut_4_1%22%20bk%3D%22deut%22%20ch%3D%224%22%20vn%3D%221%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22chapter-number%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw%22%3EDeuteronomy%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23xA0%3B%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw_ch%22%3E4%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3EMoses%20Urges%20Israel%20to%20Obey%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-ch-hd%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E1%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BAnd%20now%2C%20Israel%2C%20listen%20carefully%20to%20these%20decrees%20and%20regulations%20that%20I%20am%20about%20to%20teach%20you.%20Obey%20them%20so%20that%20you%20may%20live%2C%20so%20you%20may%20enter%20and%20occupy%20the%20land%20that%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%2C%20the%20God%20of%20your%20ancestors%2C%20is%20giving%20you.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22deut_4_2%22%20bk%3D%22deut%22%20ch%3D%224%22%20vn%3D%222%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E2%3C%2Fspan%3EDo%20not%20add%20to%20or%20subtract%20from%20these%20commands%20I%20am%20giving%20you.%20Just%20obey%20the%20commands%20of%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20your%20God%20that%20I%20am%20giving%20you.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22deut_4_3%22%20bk%3D%22deut%22%20ch%3D%224%22%20vn%3D%223%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E3%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BYou%20saw%20for%20yourself%20what%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20did%20to%20you%20at%20Baal-peor.%20There%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20your%20God%20destroyed%20everyone%20who%20had%20worshiped%20Baal%2C%20the%20god%20of%20Peor.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22deut_4_4%22%20bk%3D%22deut%22%20ch%3D%224%22%20vn%3D%224%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E4%3C%2Fspan%3EBut%20all%20of%20you%20who%20were%20faithful%20to%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20your%20God%20are%20still%20alive%20today%26%23x2014%3Bevery%20one%20of%20you.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22deut_4_5%22%20bk%3D%22deut%22%20ch%3D%224%22%20vn%3D%225%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E5%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BLook%2C%20I%20now%20teach%20you%20these%20decrees%20and%20regulations%20just%20as%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20my%20God%20commanded%20me%2C%20so%20that%20you%20may%20obey%20them%20in%20the%20land%20you%20are%20about%20to%20enter%20and%20occupy.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22deut_4_6%22%20bk%3D%22deut%22%20ch%3D%224%22%20vn%3D%226%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E6%3C%2Fspan%3EObey%20them%20completely%2C%20and%20you%20will%20display%20your%20wisdom%20and%20intelligence%20among%20the%20surrounding%20nations.%20When%20they%20hear%20all%20these%20decrees%2C%20they%20will%20exclaim%2C%20%26%23x2018%3BHow%20wise%20and%20prudent%20are%20the%20people%20of%20this%20great%20nation!%26%23x2019%3B%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22deut_4_7%22%20bk%3D%22deut%22%20ch%3D%224%22%20vn%3D%227%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E7%3C%2Fspan%3EFor%20what%20great%20nation%20has%20a%20god%20as%20near%20to%20them%20as%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20our%20God%20is%20near%20to%20us%20whenever%20we%20call%20on%20him%3F%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22deut_4_8%22%20bk%3D%22deut%22%20ch%3D%224%22%20vn%3D%228%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E8%3C%2Fspan%3EAnd%20what%20great%20nation%20has%20decrees%20and%20regulations%20as%20righteous%20and%20fair%20as%20this%20body%20of%20instructions%20that%20I%20am%20giving%20you%20today%3F%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22deut_4_9%22%20bk%3D%22deut%22%20ch%3D%224%22%20vn%3D%229%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E9%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BBut%20watch%20out!%20Be%20careful%20never%20to%20forget%20what%20you%20yourself%20have%20seen.%20Do%20not%20let%20these%20memories%20escape%20from%20your%20mind%20as%20long%20as%20you%20live!%20And%20be%20sure%20to%20pass%20them%20on%20to%20your%20children%20and%20grandchildren.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22deut_4_10%22%20bk%3D%22deut%22%20ch%3D%224%22%20vn%3D%2210%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E10%3C%2Fspan%3ENever%20forget%20the%20day%20when%20you%20stood%20before%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20your%20God%20at%20Mount%20Sinai%2C%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E4%3A10%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Hebrew%20%3Cem%3EHoreb%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20another%20name%20for%20Sinai%3B%20also%20in%204%3A15.%3C%2Fspan%3E%20where%20he%20told%20me%2C%20%26%23x2018%3BSummon%20the%20people%20before%20me%2C%20and%20I%20will%20personally%20instruct%20them.%20Then%20they%20will%20learn%20to%20fear%20me%20as%20long%20as%20they%20live%2C%20and%20they%20will%20teach%20their%20children%20to%20fear%20me%20also.%26%23x2019%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22deut_4_11%22%20bk%3D%22deut%22%20ch%3D%224%22%20vn%3D%2211%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E11%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BYou%20came%20near%20and%20stood%20at%20the%20foot%20of%20the%20mountain%2C%20while%20flames%20from%20the%20mountain%20shot%20into%20the%20sky.%20The%20mountain%20was%20shrouded%20in%20black%20clouds%20and%20deep%20darkness.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22deut_4_12%22%20bk%3D%22deut%22%20ch%3D%224%22%20vn%3D%2212%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E12%3C%2Fspan%3EAnd%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20spoke%20to%20you%20from%20the%20heart%20of%20the%20fire.%20You%20heard%20the%20sound%20of%20his%20words%20but%20didn%26%23x2019%3Bt%20see%20his%20form%3B%20there%20was%20only%20a%20voice.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22deut_4_13%22%20bk%3D%22deut%22%20ch%3D%224%22%20vn%3D%2213%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E13%3C%2Fspan%3EHe%20proclaimed%20his%20covenant%26%23x2014%3Bthe%20Ten%20Commandments%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E4%3A13%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Hebrew%20%3Cem%3Ethe%20ten%20words.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x2014%3Bwhich%20he%20commanded%20you%20to%20keep%2C%20and%20which%20he%20wrote%20on%20two%20stone%20tablets.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22deut_4_14%22%20bk%3D%22deut%22%20ch%3D%224%22%20vn%3D%2214%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E14%3C%2Fspan%3EIt%20was%20at%20that%20time%20that%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20commanded%20me%20to%20teach%20you%20his%20decrees%20and%20regulations%20so%20you%20would%20obey%20them%20in%20the%20land%20you%20are%20about%20to%20enter%20and%20occupy.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22deut_4_15%22%20bk%3D%22deut%22%20ch%3D%224%22%20vn%3D%2215%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3EA%20Warning%20against%20Idolatry%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-hd%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E15%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BBut%20be%20very%20careful!%20You%20did%20not%20see%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x2019%3Bs%20form%20on%20the%20day%20he%20spoke%20to%20you%20from%20the%20heart%20of%20the%20fire%20at%20Mount%20Sinai.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22deut_4_16%22%20bk%3D%22deut%22%20ch%3D%224%22%20vn%3D%2216%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E16%3C%2Fspan%3ESo%20do%20not%20corrupt%20yourselves%20by%20making%20an%20idol%20in%20any%20form%26%23x2014%3Bwhether%20of%20a%20man%20or%20a%20woman%2C%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22deut_4_17%22%20bk%3D%22deut%22%20ch%3D%224%22%20vn%3D%2217%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E17%3C%2Fspan%3Ean%20animal%20on%20the%20ground%2C%20a%20bird%20in%20the%20sky%2C%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22deut_4_18%22%20bk%3D%22deut%22%20ch%3D%224%22%20vn%3D%2218%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E18%3C%2Fspan%3Ea%20small%20animal%20that%20scurries%20along%20the%20ground%2C%20or%20a%20fish%20in%20the%20deepest%20sea.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22deut_4_19%22%20bk%3D%22deut%22%20ch%3D%224%22%20vn%3D%2219%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E19%3C%2Fspan%3EAnd%20when%20you%20look%20up%20into%20the%20sky%20and%20see%20the%20sun%2C%20moon%2C%20and%20stars%26%23x2014%3Ball%20the%20forces%20of%20heaven%26%23x2014%3Bdon%26%23x2019%3Bt%20be%20seduced%20into%20worshiping%20them.%20The%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20your%20God%20gave%20them%20to%20all%20the%20peoples%20of%20the%20earth.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22deut_4_20%22%20bk%3D%22deut%22%20ch%3D%224%22%20vn%3D%2220%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E20%3C%2Fspan%3ERemember%20that%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20rescued%20you%20from%20the%20iron-smelting%20furnace%20of%20Egypt%20in%20order%20to%20make%20you%20his%20very%20own%20people%20and%20his%20special%20possession%2C%20which%20is%20what%20you%20are%20today.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22deut_4_21%22%20bk%3D%22deut%22%20ch%3D%224%22%20vn%3D%2221%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E21%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BBut%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20was%20angry%20with%20me%20because%20of%20you.%20He%20vowed%20that%20I%20would%20not%20cross%20the%20Jordan%20River%20into%20the%20good%20land%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20your%20God%20is%20giving%20you%20as%20your%20special%20possession.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22deut_4_22%22%20bk%3D%22deut%22%20ch%3D%224%22%20vn%3D%2222%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E22%3C%2Fspan%3EYou%20will%20cross%20the%20Jordan%20to%20occupy%20the%20land%2C%20but%20I%20will%20not.%20Instead%2C%20I%20will%20die%20here%20on%20the%20east%20side%20of%20the%20river.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22deut_4_23%22%20bk%3D%22deut%22%20ch%3D%224%22%20vn%3D%2223%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E23%3C%2Fspan%3ESo%20be%20careful%20not%20to%20break%20the%20covenant%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20your%20God%20has%20made%20with%20you.%20Do%20not%20make%20idols%20of%20any%20shape%20or%20form%2C%20for%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20your%20God%20has%20forbidden%20this.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22deut_4_24%22%20bk%3D%22deut%22%20ch%3D%224%22%20vn%3D%2224%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E24%3C%2Fspan%3EThe%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20your%20God%20is%20a%20devouring%20fire%3B%20he%20is%20a%20jealous%20God.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22deut_4_25%22%20bk%3D%22deut%22%20ch%3D%224%22%20vn%3D%2225%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E25%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BIn%20the%20future%2C%20when%20you%20have%20children%20and%20grandchildren%20and%20have%20lived%20in%20the%20land%20a%20long%20time%2C%20do%20not%20corrupt%20yourselves%20by%20making%20idols%20of%20any%20kind.%20This%20is%20evil%20in%20the%20sight%20of%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20your%20God%20and%20will%20arouse%20his%20anger.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22deut_4_26%22%20bk%3D%22deut%22%20ch%3D%224%22%20vn%3D%2226%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E26%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BToday%20I%20call%20on%20heaven%20and%20earth%20as%20witnesses%20against%20you.%20If%20you%20break%20my%20covenant%2C%20you%20will%20quickly%20disappear%20from%20the%20land%20you%20are%20crossing%20the%20Jordan%20to%20occupy.%20You%20will%20live%20there%20only%20a%20short%20time%3B%20